  <brief_title>Evaluation of an Early Screening Test of Chronic Rejection and of Operational Tolerance by MicroArray in Renal Graft (Protocol DPRC Array)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of an Early Screening Test of Chronic Rejection and of Operational Tolerance by MicroArray in Renal Graft.</official_title>
